which averaged 18.8 USD (median = 0 USD), excluding cost of medications.
DISCUSSION: Forced displacement presents major challenges to those with NCDs, 
which have the potential to seriously impact both the quality of life and life 
expectancy amongst refugees. NCD patterns among Syrian refugees indicate the 
importance of continuing support to public sector services in Jordan to 
adequately meet expanding needs and ensure appropriate prevention and control of 
priority NCDs.

