One-year GH replacement therapy reduces early cardiac target organ damage (TOD) 
in adult GHD patients.

Boschetti M(1)(2), Agosti S(3), Albanese V(4), Casalino L(3), Teti C(4), Bezante 
GP(3), Brunelli C(3), Albertelli M(4)(5), Ferone D(4)(5).

